Prime Collins Street retail / showroom opportunity in the heart of Collins Street surrounded by some of the best local & national hospitality & service tenants.

Key Features: 

- High foot traffic 7 days per week 

- Rear lane access to Manchester Lane 

- Flexible terms being offered

- Double frontage onto Collins Street and Manchester Lane. 

- Optimum branding 

- Available now

+ Situated on one of Melbourne’s most high-profile retail corners Collins Street and Swanston Street within Melbourne’s famed Manchester Unity Building

+ Fully leased investment returning $300,000 p.a net* to ‘Invisalign by Smile Solutions’ backed by renowned brand Smile Solutions

+ Offering a brand new 7 + 7-year lease to market leader with over 25 years of operation - largest single location dental practice in Australia

+ High exposure corner tenancy with multiple access points through Manchester Unity Arcade

+ Irreplaceable Collins Street address with unrivalled public transport connectivity with Collins Street tram stop directly out the front of the property and Flinders Street Train Station within 150 metres* walking distance

+ Uniquely positioned to benefit from the $11 billion Metro Tunnel project with entry to the new Town Hall Train Station on the parallel corner of Collins Street set for completion in 2024
